#
#  PGML 
#
#

BEGIN_PGML

[@ image("UBC-SM-18-072.png", width=>[$width], height=>[$height]) @]*

A uniform steel pipe is rigidly fixed at both ends. Initially, the pipe is stress-free. An axial force of [`[$load]`] [`lb`] is applied [`x=[$l]`] [`ft`] from one end, as shown in the diagram. What is the reaction force at each end ? For the pipe, [`L = [$lt]`] [`ft`] ,[`D_{inner} = [$di]`][`"`], [`D_{outer} = [$do]`][`"`], [`E = 30 \cdot 10^6`] [`psi`], [`\nu = 0.3`].  
_Hint: Choose the information you need_. 


[`R_A=`] [____]{"$ra"} [`lb`]  
[`R_C=`] [____]{"$rc"} [`lb`]  

